map f navigate next
map b navigate previous
map <C--> zoom out
map <C-s> zoom out
map <C-+> zoom in
map <C-w> zoom in
map <C-b> adjust_window best-fit
map <C-W> adjust_window width

# invert (<C-r> to invert invert)
